# Full URLs for content and structure monitoring (one per line).
# AssetMonitor will crawl these URLs, hash page content, diff DOM structure,
# track endpoints, and detect technology stack changes on every scan cycle.
#
# Use full URLs including the scheme (https:// or http://).
# Lines starting with # are treated as comments and ignored.
#
# Example entries:
https://example.com
https://app.example.com
https://admin.example.com/login
https://api.example.com/v1
